# Legacy C++ Loan Calculator (Refactored)

## Build Instructions
g++ -std=c++11 LoanCalculator.cpp -o calc

## Run
./calc 

## Description
This project is an improved version of a legacy-style loan/EMI calculator.
Fixes include:
- Input validation
- Overflow protection
- Configuration loaded from config.txt
- Refactored into src/ folder
- Unit tests using GoogleTest
- Documented with Doxygen
- Added a EMI Calculator function in seperate file

